cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as Chinese word segmentation and POS tagging. The use of deep learning architectures also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of convolutional and pooling layers suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) as well. Finally, the use of recurrent layers suggests that it could belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
